    %h1{align: "center"}
      Build predictive models faster than ever before.
    %p
      <strong>Syberia</strong> is a framework for quickly trying different methods in data science.  Syberia supports building, debugging, testing, and deploying classifiers developed in R.
    %p
      Syberia includes support for importing data, preparing data, multiple statistical modeling methodologies, exporting trained classifiers, validating the results, and deploying as a REST service.  Syberia makes it easy to <strong>quickly clean up messy data</strong>, build <strong>produciton-ready predictive models</strong>, and quickly <strong>skip past the boring stuff and onto the interesting data analysis.</strong>
    %p{align: "center"}
      %button{:id => "start_button", :class => "btn btn-primary btn-large", :type => "submit"}
